Privacy Policy — WealthFolio
Last updated: 28 June 2026
WealthFolio ("the app") is an offline-first portfolio, dividend and capital-gains
tracker for the Pakistan Stock Exchange. This policy explains what data the app
handles.
What we store
Your portfolio data — trades, dividends, cash flows, watchlist, prices and
settings — is stored only on your device. We do not run a server that
receives or holds this data by default.
What we do not collect ourselves
We do not collect your contacts, location, or your portfolio for ourselves.
We use no analytics of our own.
No account is required to use the app's core features.
Advertising (Google AdMob)
The app displays ads using Google AdMob. To serve and measure ads, Google may
collect and process certain device information and identifiers (such as your
advertising ID) in accordance with Google's Privacy Policy
(https://policies.google.com/privacy) and the Google Play services terms. You can
reset or limit your advertising ID in your device settings
(Settings → Privacy → Ads).
Internet use
The app works offline for its core features. It connects to the internet only for:
Ads — to load ads via Google AdMob (see above).
Live share prices — when you open Holdings or tap refresh, the app requests
current prices from the public Pakistan Stock Exchange data portal
(`dps.psx.com.pk`). Only public market prices are fetched; no personal data is
sent.
Cloud Backup & Sync (optional) — only if you choose to sign in, the app uses
Supabase to store a backup of your portfolio under your account:
We process the email address you sign up with (for authentication).
We store a copy of your portfolio data so you can sync it across devices.
Only your authenticated account can read or write it. You can delete it any
time by removing your backup or deleting your account.
If you never sign in, your portfolio never leaves your device.
Data sharing
We do not sell your data. Data is processed only by the services involved in the
features you use: Google AdMob (ads), the PSX data portal (public prices),
and Supabase (only if you enable Cloud Sync).
Data retention & deletion
On-device data is removed when you uninstall the app or use the in-app reset.
Cloud backups (if you created any) remain until you delete them or your account.
Children
The app is not directed at children under 13 and does not knowingly collect data
from them.
Disclaimer
All figures (returns, dividends, capital gains and tax estimates) are for your
information only and are not financial, tax or investment advice.
